name: The Fluffy Skull (4K)
description:
I am an award winning metaverse builder, this is one of my earlier designs in 3D. 

Skulls are normally portrayed with darkness, but its part of our vehicle through life. I also believe its signification to death is seen as a bad thing, but moving on to our next journey is about letting go of the past and onwards to a bright future (if you believe in life after death that is).

Hope you enjoy.
